c: 7
v: 179
t: "Kandi ntankeka twarabaremeye umuriro witiriwe Jahannama, benshi mubisigo no mu bantu, bakaba bafise imitima mugabo ntibategera, n’amaso barayafise mugabo ntibabona n’amatwi barayafise mugabo ntibumva, abo bantu ni nk’ibikoko ahubwo n’abantu bazimiye cane, kandi nibo ataco bibuka nagatoyi"